mg src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493db7057f060dba61a0552ced7e5247117e99ed","tid":2393661,"uid":17335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e061da78e4c7ddc82503ce6f0a0152502ff764b5","tid":2393661,"uid":66546,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:23:21.000Z","msg":"暗殺教室個風格好特別 <br />\n超好笑得嚟仲要每集都有唔同學生嘅故事<br />\n最後個結局好感人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 碧池sen sei<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結局其實好好，死得好完滿<br />\n每集學生都被殺老師因材施教<br />\n正經得嚟好輕鬆"},{"pid":"7604ca37296efedd2ec39a839dab31af1e878f2d","tid":2393661,"uid":17335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00d727e9cfeda29a1cb1ed2d21ecb826ce411738","tid":2393661,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"同三年a班相映成趣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"呢套正在，因為有3年A班<br />\n所以佢哋兩堆人先可以互相成長<br />\n校長個仔都好有自己諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea584d679f30a13a8c054363559ffb35ee3cf0b","tid":2393661,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"呢套係我心目中No.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結局完得好靚 每個故事都好深刻好有意思<br />\n教咗我好多好多成長嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2732f8357154aa8a3f523747b066e21be2ab570","tid":2393661,"uid":17335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"56893a5139d9e89623f9df8f23ba7ed1998a81ec","tid":2393661,"uid":220458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"我係睇漫畫嘅<br />\n個結局突登草埋睇<br />\n望住又原本救到<br />\n但無奈一定要落手殺佢個下<br />\n喊撚到我仆街<br />\n好記得個晚同親戚食飯<br />\n一路要忍撚住<br />\n但嘅眼淚又一路滲出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇到最後已經估到無咁易完<br />\n救到反而令成件事仲催淚<br />\n不過死作為生命教育，都係完滿嘅一堂<br />\n最後死得好靚，呢位老師竟然做到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5335cf8e2045c51c6f11e286da7fe681520dcd1","tid":2393661,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"樓主會唔會講下《進擊的巨人》<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b661a3cc98d173df6753022efcad54fc73408600","tid":2393661,"uid":49057,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a5bf2edda0798f215e01c12a7759f341c1754977","tid":2393661,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"a49c1ca7e9c2a69e18c48ab9c9f3b29a6d22c0c0","tid":2393661,"uid":199617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"樓主連動漫都有涉獵<br />\n<br />\n暗殺教室真係少有<br />\n幾搞笑，而且正向得嚟又唔會太說教，係好理想嘅少年漫畫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />漫畫、動漫都好好睇<br />\n暗殺教室呢套絕對可以係教師、學生必睇<br />\n等大家知道教育其實都仲有理想<img s